\p{XmacsLabs is a non-profit organization dedicated to creating open-source tools for exploring science and technology. The team collaborates on projects for structured editing, programming, and scientific publishing.}

\ul{
  \li{[[Mogan_STEM]]: a structured editor based on GNU TeXmacs (Stable)}
  \li{Mogan Language: a structured programming language (Designing)}
  \li{Xmacs Planet: public docs by the Xmacs community (Beta)}
  \li{TMML Wiki: wiki of Science and Technology (Alpha)}
}

\p{XmacsLabs also maintains open structured text projects such as [《Mozi》](https://gitee.com/XmacsLabs/mozi) (Simplified Chinese) and [《Interactive SICP》](https://gitee.com/XmacsLabs/interactive-sicp) (English).}
